            "title": "在岸人民幣兌美元收升54點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">在岸人民幣兑美元官方收報6.9636，較上日收盤升54點。</p>\n</div>",
