            "title": "全日收市︱成交縮減 恒指跌281點報26563點 「ATMXJ」齊跌 滙控全程「潛水」",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股午後未見太大起色，雖然未再跌穿早市低位，但亦一直在10天線下徘徊。「ATMXJ」與滙控(00005)為首重磅金融股，均有份拖低大市。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20231031_FI_source-web_00005.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20231031_FI_source-web_00005.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：滙控官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數今早低開203點後持續弱勢，初段最低曾見26533點，跌311點，隨著內地公布去年經濟增長等多項主要數據，港股跌幅曾收窄至129點、報26715點，其後再度反覆調整，跌幅重新擴大至逾200點，失守10天線(最新約為26634點)直至收市。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20231031_FI_source-web_00005.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20231031_FI_source-web_00005.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：滙控官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股11.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股11.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：港交所官網影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/00388-4.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：港交所官網影片截圖\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/00388-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：港交所官網影片截圖</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240619_FI_source-web_09988-2.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240619_FI_source-web_09988-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"優必選官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/09880-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"優必選官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/09880-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">優必選官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"中國生物製藥官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/01177-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"中國生物製藥官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/01177-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">中國生物製藥官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20231031_FI_source-web_00005.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：滙控官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股11.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：港交所官網影片截圖\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/00388-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：港交所官網影片截圖</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240619_FI_source-web_09988-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"優必選官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/09880-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">優必選官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"中國生物製藥官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/01177-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">中國生物製藥官網</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒指最後收報26563點，跌281點或1.05%。恒生科技指數跑輸大市，收跌72點或1.24%，報5749點；國企指數跌86點或0.94%，報9134點。主板成交進一步縮減至2256.89億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指跌241點或0.9%，報26588點，高水24點。科指期貨跌66點或1.13%，報5755點，高水5點。國指期貨跌70點或0.76%，報9145點，高水11點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股11.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股11.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大市今日跌勢頗為全面，88隻恒指成分股中多達66隻報跌，即有四分之三收跌，其中兩大藍籌國際金融股均全日「潛水」，成功將恒生銀行(00011)的滙控，暫停之前4日的連升紀錄，今日最高僅見127.5元，仍跌0.78%；收報127元，跌1.17%。友邦(01299)今日高位83.4元時也跌0.18%；收報82.95元，跌0.72%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股交投進一步減少，港交所(00388)今日亦借勢再回，收報431.8元，跌1.51%。單計滙控、友邦與港交所，合共已拖低恒指逾51點。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：港交所官網影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/00388-4.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：港交所官網影片截圖\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/00388-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：港交所官網影片截圖</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">重磅科股亦跌多升少，上周累計升逾13%的阿里巴巴(09988)，雖然有集團首席執行官吳泳銘發表新年家書，明言集團去年幾場「大仗」都打得漂亮，該股今日依然逃不過裂口回吐的命運。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">阿里巴巴今早甫開市即挫2.53%，報162元，全日高位亦僅162.5元，最低曾見160.1元，挫3.67%；收報160.4元，跌3.49%，單一股份已令恒指跌逾77點。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">「ATMXJ」其餘4位成員同樣向下，跌幅更均超過1%。小米(01810)持續近期弱勢，收跌1.67%，報36.48元；騰訊(00700)跌1.22%，報610元；京東(09618)跌1.14%，報112.3元。上周險守百元關的美團(03690)，今早甫開市已離開「紅底股」行列，收報98.5元，跌1.5%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240619_FI_source-web_09988-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240619_FI_source-web_09988-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上周落實發行美元及人民幣優先票據的快手(01024)，今日更跌2.04%，報76.75元。芯片股回軟，中芯(00981)跌2.78%，報77元；華虹半導體(01347)跌3.93%，報102.6元。平台經濟股嗶哩嗶哩(09626)挫6.85%，報242.2元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">亦有個別重磅科股逆市造好，百度(09888)幾乎全日逆市報升，收報147.4元，升1.24%；網易(09999)也升0.28%，報216.2元。涉壟斷遭市場監管總局立案調查消息於上周曝光後，股價隨即急挫的攜程(09961)，今日再反彈0.9%，報470.4元；近期弱勢的泡泡瑪特(09992)也升1.23%，報180.8元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">機器人概念更明顯受捧，優必選(09880)據報與Airbus達成人形機械人在航空製造領域合作，股價創1個月高位，收報144.7元，漲8.63%；越疆(02432)升0.72%，報39.34元；地平線機器人(09660)升0.21%，報9.39元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"優必選官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/09880-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"優必選官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/09880-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">優必選官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上周訪華的加拿大總理卡尼宣布，將以6.1%的最惠國稅率進口4.9萬輛內地電動汽車，意味著加拿大結束對內地電動汽車加徵100%關稅措施，恢復到貿易摩擦前的關稅水平。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地車企應聲則個別發展，比亞迪(01211)重越百元關，報100.7元，升1.51%；蔚來(09866)升0.27%，報36.74元；零跑汽車(09863)微升0.22%，報44.92元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">相反，小鵬汽車(09868)則跌0.44%，報80.1元；理想汽車(02015)也跌0.4%，報62.55元；吉利汽車(00175)跌0.58%，報17.03元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">生科藥業板塊午後持續弱勢，表現最差5隻藍籌中有4隻是藥股，中國生物製藥(011770挫6.19%，報6.52元；上周遭股東配股套現逾57億元的藥明生物(02269)，今日再%，報37.86元；信達生物(01801)跌4.64%，報85.35元；翰森製藥(03692)跌4%，報41.28元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"中國生物製藥官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/01177-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"中國生物製藥官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/01177-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">中國生物製藥官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">在少數逆市報升的藍籌中，也有兩隻升上52周新高，包括後來居上成為表現最佳恒指成分股的中國石化(00386)，收報4.95元，升3.34%；李寧(02331)跌落藍籌升幅榜次席，升2.94%，以21元收市。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">另外，不少盈喜股也逆市炒上，趣致集團(00917)料去年扭虧為盈，股價飆38.78%，報35元；TCL電子(01070)料去年淨利增起碼45%，股價今日即漲13.4%，報11.17元；中國太平(00966)今日中午發盈喜公告，料去年純利升最少2.15倍，該股午後隨即抽升6.44%，收報22.8元，創逾3年新高。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15594476-%e5%85%a8%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e6%88%90%e4%ba%a4%e7%b8%ae%e6%b8%9b-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e8%b7%8c281%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b126563%e9%bb%9e-%e3%80%8catmxj%e3%80%8d%e9%bd%8a%e8%b7%8c-%e6%bb%99",
